ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDESIGNATED BARLEY- 2010-2011 UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2011-2012 Pool **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the DESIGNATED BARLEY unsold from the preceding pool, that began on August 1, 2010 and ended on July 31, 2011 to the current pool period, that began August 1, 2011 and will end July 31, 2012.
